The paper deals with linear precoding in MISO broadcast channels with confidential messages, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses the optimization of network load and regularization parameter, which falls under the category of mathematical modeling (cs.MM). The concept of secrecy in communication is also a topic of interest in security and privacy (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the impact of channel state information (CSI) error, which is a topic related to networked systems (cs.NI) and communication engineering (cs.CE).
